# Use the following steps when user asks to build something
1. Crete a new feature branch
2. Write the tests using Pytest
3. Run the tests using Pytest and make sure they run and fail
4. Write the code for the feature
5. Run linter ruff check .
6. Format code ruff format .
7. Run tests again and make sure they pass now
8. Make a commit that will trigger pre-commit hooks
9. Give a summary to the user
